data.description:
The open floorplan home with no carpet, no HOA, high ceilings, arched doorways, and rounded corners. Spa-like master bath with spacious walk-in closets. Granite countertops,  stove, dishwasher, and microwave.  Great backyard. Close to schools and shopping. Ask about financing options.  Includes washer and dryer.

Open house Saturday January 5th 1:00 pm-3:00 pm and Sunday January 6th 1:00-3:00 pm
